 Sion|Sion]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.juventusnews24.com/juve-primavera-cotter-giugno-prestito-sion/|title=Juve Primavera, Cotter in arrivo a giugno: resta in prestito al Sion|first=Redazione|last=JuventusNews24|date=9 January 2020}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|pos=MF|nat=NED|name=[[Leandro Fernandes]]|other=at {{flagicon|NED}} [[Fortuna Sittard]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ilbianconero.com/a/accordo-trovato-leandro-fernandes-saluta-la-juve-66635|title=Accordo trovato: Leandro Fernandes saluta la Juve|website=Juventus News - Ultime Notizie Juve - il BiancoNero}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=MF|nat=ITA|name=[[Nicol\u00f2 Francofonte]]|other=at [[U.C. Sampdoria|Sampdoria]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref name=\"ReferenceA\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-a/ufficiale-samp-prelevati-stoppa-francofonte-e-gerbi-dalla-juventus-1343559|title=UFFICIALE: Samp, prelevati Stoppa, Francofonte e Gerbi dalla Juventus - TUTTOmercatoWEB.com|website=www.tuttomercatoweb.com}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=MF|nat=CYP|name=[[Grigoris Kastanos]]|other=at [[Delfino Pescara 1936|Pescara]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tuttomercatoweb.com/serie-b/ufficiale-pescara-colpo-kastanos-preso-in-prestito-dalla-juve-1282867|title=UFFICIALE: Pescara, colpo Kastanos. Preso in prestito dalla Juve - TUTTOmercatoWEB.com|website=www.tuttomercatoweb.com}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|no=|pos=MF|nat=SWE|name=[[Dejan Kulusevski]]|other=at [[Parma Calcio 1913|Parma]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.juventus.com/it/news/news/2020/dejan-kulusevski---un-giocatore-della-juventus-.php|title=Dejan Kulusevski \u00e8 un giocatore della Juventus!|website=Juventus.com|access-date=2 January 2020}}</ref>\n{{Fs player|pos=MF|nat=FRA|name=[[K\u00e9vin Monzialo]]|other=at {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Grasshopper Club Z\u00fcrich|Grasshopper]] until 30 June 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://onefootball.com/it/notizie/monzialo-al-grasshopper-e-ufficiale-